verse impacts on the luminescence. Furthermore, our\nconclusions highlight the influence the dielectric properties of the substrate\nhave on the luminescence of WSe$_2$, showing that a low electrical permittivity\nfavours preserving the native properties of the adjacent monolayer\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2023 21:58:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-17"}
