the line. For\nthe interpretation of transit observations, it is crucial for model spectra\nthat accurately reproduce the solar CLV to become available which, for now, is\nthe only calibration point available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 09:23:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
