}\\approx3.85$ $\\mathrm{fW}$ for $x=1.5$ with\nthe same efficiency as that of the symmetric case.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 10:24:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-17"}
