s. Finally, an extension of the\nasymptotic analysis of Callegari and Ting [J. App. Math (1978)] is carried out\nto include the effect of gravity. The results show that, in the regime\nconsidered here, a contribution from the gravity term occurs only when the tail\nof an infinitely long filament is tilted at an angle relative to the wall.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2023 13:24:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-17"}
